    "questbook.astrogreg.ulv.progression.introduction.description_0": "Welcome to the Kuiper Belt! You've probably noticed that you've spawned in the middle of a field of asteroids, but thankfully the §4ASTRO Foundation§r has provided you with everything you need to survive here.",
    "questbook.astrogreg.ulv.progression.introduction.description_1": "You can fill your company-issued space suit in the top right slot of the oxygen diffuser to the left of your emergency survival kit.",
    "questbook.astrogreg.ulv.progression.familiar_start.description_0": "The next step in being able to explore your environment will require you grow a tree.",
    "questbook.astrogreg.ulv.progression.familiar_start.description_1": "You can make space for it by breaking a block in the floor and replacing it with dirt from your emergency survival kit.",
    "questbook.astrogreg.ulv.progression.iron_man.description_0": "Now that you're properly equipped, it's time for you to go collect some asteroid stone for a stone pickaxe. Once you do, you can start collecting ores like iron ore and other useful ores.",
    "questbook.astrogreg.ulv.progression.iron_man.description_1": "Don't worry too much about falling into the void, you'll loop back around eventually.",
    "questbook.astrogreg.ulv.progression.wrought_iron_man.description_0": "With a campfire and a little you'll be able to convert your iron ingots into wrought iron, serving as a stronger alternative to iron for making tools.",
    "questbook.astrogreg.ulv.progression.bronze_materials.description_0": "Optionally, you can jump right in to the Steam Age if you would like, it just means that you would need to collect the materials for bronze first.",
    "questbook.astrogreg.ulv.progression.bronze_materials.description_1": "This will require you to collect copper ore for copper and cassiterite ore for tin.",

